graph [
   citation "['S. Aref and M. C. Wilson, &quot;Balance and frustration in signed networks.&quot; J. Complex Networks 7(2), 163–189 (2019), https://doi.org/10.1093/comnet/cny015']"
   description "Fifteen networks of carbon atoms and the atomic bonds that connect them within molecules of fullerenes, from 60 atoms up to 6000 atoms. A bond is defined to exist whenever the distance of two atoms is less than 1.5 angstrom."
